                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Shh — you'll scare it! …Aw. It went under the boardwalk. The blue ones only come out at dusk, and they never let me catch up."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Da says the wisps are just marsh-light. But marsh-light doesn't WAIT for you at the bend. Hey — trainers carry glimmery ones, don't they? The pink-sparkly kind? Show me one! Just once!"
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Bryn — chasing wisps",
                    Label: "default"
